  decomposition: (97 769) (&#39;a&#39; &#39;ÃÅ&#39;)
...</code></pre></div>
<p>This can be specially usefull in our emojis, let's try it on ‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•:</p>
<div class="remark-highlight"><pre class="language-text"><code class="language-text">			 position: 8529 of 10012 (85%), column: 61
			character: ‚ù§ (displayed as ‚ù§) (codepoint 10084, #o23544, #x2764)
